CREATE TABLE airbnb.bookings_fact (
    booking_id NVARCHAR(100),
    property_id NVARCHAR(100),
    customer_id INT,
    owner_id NVARCHAR(100),
    check_in_date DATE,
    check_out_date DATE,
    booking_date DATETIME,
    amount FLOAT,
    currency NVARCHAR(10),
    city NVARCHAR(100),
    country NVARCHAR(100),
    full_address NVARCHAR(255),
    stay_duration BIGINT,
    booking_year INT,
    booking_month INT,
    timestamp DATETIME
);

SELECT * FROM airbnb.bookings_fact;

SELECT * FROM airbnb.bookings_fact WHERE booking_id = 'c1fc48f6-b35a-4910-858d-98803900ad53';

DBCC FREEPROCCACHE;

TRUNCATE TABLE airbnb.bookings_fact;
